    <abstract id="Abs2" abstract-type="web-summary">
      <p>The genome sequence is presented for the Atlantic salmon (Salmo salar), providing information about a rediploidization following a salmonid-specific whole-genome duplication event that resulted in an autotetraploidization.</p>
